data.enText: to waste money, time, etc. in a stupid or careless way

data.chText: 他把自己所有的钱都糟蹋在赌博上了。
data.enText: He squandered all his money on gambling.

example: He wasted his inheritance on his insincere friends
You squandered the opportunity to get and advanced degree

value.def: If you squander money, resources, or opportunities, you waste them.

example.ex: Hooker didn't squander his money on flashy cars or other vices...
example.tran: 胡克没有将自己的钱浪费在豪华轿车或其他恶习上。

example.ex: He had squandered his chances to win.
example.tran: 他白白浪费了获胜的机会。

value.tran: 浪费，挥霍(金钱、资源、机遇等)
